\f0\fs28\li2200 Abstract superclass for Text Attributes, as used by the {\b Text} and the {\b RunArray} classes.\fs16\
\
\f0\fs28\li2200 Typically, an application will subclass {\b TextAttribute} and use its own subclass with the {\b Text} instance method {\f2 addAttribute:}.\fs16\
