\f1\b\fs28\li2200 emphasiscode:\f0\b0\
\f0\fs28\li2500 +{\b emphasiscode}:(unsigned){\i n}\fs16\
\
\f0\fs28\li2200 A Text Attribute instance with emphasiscode set to {\i n}.  This value may suffice for simple applications, but normally a subclass of {\b TextAttribute} would be used to associate more sophisticated values to a Text Attribute (such as URL of a hypertext link, or such as a Color value, or an X-Windows font etc.).\fs16\
\
\fs16\
